            </style>
            <main id="wrap" class="drift-sku">
                <section class="drift-sku__hero">
                    <div class="drift-sku__copy">
                        <p class="drift-sku__eyebrow">DRIFT Sauna Hat</p>
                        <h1>The uniform for controlled heat.</h1>
                        <p class="drift-sku__lead">A wool sauna hat for athletes who use heat as a deliberate end to the training day. Low-tech, visible, and made for the moment training turns into downshift.</p>
                        <div class="drift-sku__actions">
                            <t t-if="variant_id">
                                <form class="drift-sku__form" t-att-action="'/drift/shop/add/%s' % product.id" method="post">
                                    <input type="hidden" name="csrf_token" t-att-value="request.csrf_token()"/>
                                    <button type="submit">Add Sauna Hat</button>
                                </form>
                            </t>
                            <t t-else="">
                                <a class="drift-sku__button" t-att-href="product_url">Shop Sauna Hat</a>
                            </t>
                            <a class="drift-sku__button drift-sku__button--ghost" t-att-href="product_url">View details</a>
                            <span class="drift-sku__price" t-if="price_label"><t t-out="price_label"/></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <aside class="drift-sku__panel">
                        <p class="drift-sku__eyebrow">Founding batch</p>
                        <strong>First 100 sauna sessions.</strong>
                        <p>Wear it, log the Sauna Downshift, and help shape Batch 002. DRIFT is built from field notes, not generic recovery noise.</p>
                    </aside>
                </section>

                <section class="drift-sku__band">
                    <p class="drift-sku__eyebrow">Why it works</p>
                    <h2>A clear object for a clear ritual.</h2>
                    <div class="drift-sku__grid">
                        <article class="drift-sku__card">
                            <span>01 / Ritual</span>
                            <h3>Heat has a visible uniform.</h3>
                            <p>The hat marks the shift from output to downshift: phone away, pace lower, session intentional.</p>
                        </article>
                        <article class="drift-sku__card">
                            <span>02 / Heat</span>
                            <h3>Made for the hot room.</h3>
                            <p>Simple wool construction, clean profile, and no loud graphic language. It belongs in the routine.</p>
                        </article>
                        <article class="drift-sku__card">
                            <span>03 / System</span>
                            <h3>Keeps the habit going.</h3>
                            <p>Pair it with DRIFT to log heat sessions, keep streaks, and follow the Sauna Downshift program.</p>
                        </article>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section class="drift-sku__split">
                    <div>
                        <p class="drift-sku__eyebrow">Sauna Downshift</p>
                        <h2>Run hard. Breathe down. Close the day.</h2>
                        <p>DRIFT sells the ritual, not just the wool. The hat is the anchor for a simple post-training sequence: enter heat calmly, stay intentional, cool down, and log the session when it is done.</p>
                        <div class="drift-sku__actions">
                            <a class="drift-sku__button" t-att-href="kit_url">Shop Downshift Kit</a>
